	  <concept id="i1106106"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">15.403-5</ph> Instructions for submission of certified cost or pricing data and data other than certified cost or pricing data.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d908e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d922e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Taking into consideration the policy at <xref href="FAR-i1105907.dita#i1105907"
                        base="i1105907"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15.402</xref>, the contracting officer shall specify in the solicitation (see <xref href="FAR-i1106593.dita#i1106593"
                        base="i1106593"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">15.408</xref>(l) and (m))-</p>
					          <ol id="d908e29" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e33" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Whether certified cost or pricing data are required;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                That, in lieu of submitting certified cost or pricing data, the offeror may submit a request for exception from the requirement to submit certified cost or pricing data;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Any requirement for data other than certified cost or pricing data; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e60" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The requirement for necessary preaward or postaward access to offeror’s records.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d922e71" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d908e77" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e81" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Format for submission of certified cost or pricing data</i>. When certification is required, the contracting officer may require submission of certified cost or pricing data in the format indicated in <xref href="FAR-i1106593.dita#i1106593/i1106753"
                              base="i1106753"
                              outputclass="fm:Table"
                              class="- topic/xref ">Table  15-2</xref> of <xref href="FAR-i1106593.dita#i1106593"
                              base="i1106593"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">15.408</xref>, specify an alternative format, or permit submission in the contractor’s format (See <xref href="FAR-i1106593.dita#i1106593"
                              base="i1106593"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">15.408</xref>(l)(1)), unless the data are required to be submitted on one of the termination forms specified in <xref href="FAR-i1067220.dita#i1067220"
                              base="i1067220"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  49.6</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e106" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Format for submission of data other than certified cost or pricing data</i>. When required by the contracting officer, data other than certified cost or pricing data may be submitted in the offeror’s own format unless the contracting officer decides that use of a specific format is essential for evaluating and determining that the price is fair and reasonable and the format has been described in the solicitation.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d922e118" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                
								                <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Format for submission of data supporting forward pricing rate agreements</i>. Data supporting forward pricing rate agreements or final indirect cost proposals shall be submitted in a form acceptable to the contracting officer.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
